      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Oracle XStream CDC Connector Logs\n\n**Prerequisites:** [Loki](https://grafana.com/oss/loki/) + Promtail. With `docker/docker-compose.monitoring.yml`, **Loki** and **Promtail** are included; Promtail ships the **connect** container logs with `job=kafka-connect`.\n\n**Without that compose:** use a Loki Docker logging driver or run Promtail with access to `/var/run/docker.sock`."
      },
      "title": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "axisPlacement": "auto" },
          "unit": "short"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({job=\"kafka-connect\"} |= \"ERROR\" [$__interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "ERROR logs",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({job=\"kafka-connect\"} |= \"WARN\" [$__interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "WARN logs",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Kafka Connect - Error & Warning Rate",
      "description": "Count of ERROR and WARN log entries over time",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
